name: Party Decorations
description:
Simple, we have a set of 3 hand made party decorations!

1x pack of paper bunting, featuring alternating vintage map paper hearts and vintage style "cat" paper flags

1x pack of paper confetti mainly featuring origami hearts

1x pack of hand painted pegs, for hanging your bunting or pegging balloons to stuff!

All your party needs in one place!!

Any questions please let me know.

name: Vintage Tea Cup Candle
description:
A gorgeous, blue Doulton, vintage, tea cup candle!

Hand made in Winchester... the perfect gift!

Any questions, big or small please do let me know!

name: Lime Green Vintage Chalkboard
description:
Mr Limey is up for sale... finally!! 

He measures 31cm by 26cm and has been lovingly painted in a gorgeous lime green, distressed a little for the shabby chic look and waxed to protect him!

Mr Limey started life as a vintage picture frame, his glass has been removed and his inside painted in chalkboard paint so you can write as many messages as you want!

He is a standing frame but just let me know if you would like to to add some hooks and string so you can hand him up!

Any questions big or small please let me know.

name: Mini Paper Bunting - Floral
description:
Our mini paper bunting is handmade in Winchester, using upcycled new and vintage papers, strung onto a length of twine measuring 2 meters.. or there about!

Perfect for parties of the, tea, garden or birthday variety or just to hang up around your home all year round.

This particular product features alternate flags of beautiful, floral recycled wrapping paper, in red, yellow and green. If you would like any more pictures please do let me know.

Happy shopping!!
